{"tid":1229510,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"花墟極有心花店巴打店主 大家之後買花記得嚟呢度","createTime":"2019-06-16T03:13:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T02:41:19.000Z","uid":68035,"like":78,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f40343448fe3e4e00f6ab2f412a31f5551b42f94","tid":1229510,"uid":68035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:13:15.000Z","msg":"頭先入呢間花店諗住問呢束6枝白菊幾多錢啦 然後位巴打店主話40蚊 我地覺得價錢好合理決定扑錘買啦 (ps其他花店都成10蚊枝但朵花好細) 然後巴打店主見到我地已經拎住幾束白菊就問「你地拎去金鐘？」 我地話係 跟住巴打店主雲淡風輕地講左句「咁你地攞去啦」<br />\n<br />\n呢位巴打店主雖然覺得自己做嘅野無咩大不了 但我見到香港人係愛呢個地方同住响同一片土地上嘅人 大家之後要多多支呢間小店 ps呢度嘅白菊暫時無曬啦 之後大家再嚟幫襯過<br />\n#香港加油<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gwFQh0q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgwFQh0q.png&h=ec21e65f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cUcZVM6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcUcZVM6.png&h=d192e1ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b571900e59452161fbab5d0c0a27400945c65134","tid":1229510,"uid":31946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:15:43.000Z","msg":"Book marked, 一陣過去買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf210834c0cda5e1d492fbc668ec1277766f2661","tid":1229510,"uid":197441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:17:28.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"362be04bf29a64193825a9b8523d36f2a6ed5204","tid":1229510,"uid":251925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:18:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a73eff931eedbd0764f58b1284f9fb07445fb93f","tid":1229510,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:18:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fa0054932896ed5de94dc15a28deaf7ae76126de","tid":1229510,"uid":61688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:20:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"77c04214fb11982ea